### Test Events API

### 1. Create Event (Organizer/Admin only)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "title": "Tech Conference 2024",
  "description": "Annual technology conference featuring latest innovations",
  "category": "technology",
  "type": "offline",
  "venue": "Addis Ababa Convention Center",
  "venueDetails": "Main Hall, 2nd Floor",
  "location": {
    "lat": 9.0054,
    "lng": 38.7636,
    "address": "Addis Ababa, Ethiopia"
  },
  "startAt": "2024-06-15T09:00:00Z",
  "endAt": "2024-06-15T17:00:00Z",
  "capacity": 500,
  "price": 1500,
  "registrationDeadline": "2024-06-10T23:59:59Z",
  "status": "published",
  "tags": ["technology", "innovation", "networking"]
}

### 2. Get All Events (Public)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/events

### 3. Get Events with Filters
GET http://localhost:3001/api/events?q=tech&category=technology&type=offline&minPrice=1000&maxPrice=2000&sort=latest&page=1&limit=5

### 4. Get Events by Location
GET http://localhost:3001/api/events?location=Addis Ababa

### 5. Get Events by Date Range
GET http://localhost:3001/api/events?startFrom=2024-06-01&startTo=2024-06-30

### 6. Get Single Event
GET http://localhost:3001/api/events/EVENT_ID

### 7. Update Event (Owner only)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/api/events/EVENT_ID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "title": "Updated Tech Conference 2024",
  "price": 1200
}

### 8. Delete Event (Owner only)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/events/EVENT_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### 9. Get My Events (Organizer/Admin only)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/events/my-events
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### 10. Upload Banner Image
POST http://localhost:3001/api/uploads
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

# Use form-data with key "file" and select an image file

### 11. Sort Events by Price (Ascending)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/events?sort=price_asc

### 12. Sort Events by Popularity
GET http://localhost:3001/api/events?sort=popular

### 13. Get Free Events
GET http://localhost:3001/api/events?maxPrice=0

### 14. Get Online Events
GET http://localhost:3001/api/events?type=online